SUMMARY:Steve Flemming's Love Songs that Stir the Soul (Thursday March 12th) 
DESCRIPTION:Soul City Social Club (Toronto\, Canada)\nHello everyone\,\n\nPlease join us **on zoom** for a fun\, relaxing and inspiring evening with **Love Songs that Stir the Soul.**\n\nSongs that I have written for well over 36 years.\nYou will love what you hear! :)\nNew songs every week\, including some of our favorites!\n\n\\*You are welcome to join us any time after 8:30 pm (Eastern Time)\n\\*You are also welcome to come on later in the evening as well\n**\\*\\*Attend for free if you like - if it's your first time attending :)**\n\nEvent Details below:\n\nSincerely\,\n\nSteve Flemming\n(Songwriter/Producer/Host)\n\nEvent Details:\n**Steve Flemming's Love Songs that Stir the Soul (Thursday\, March 12th)**\n**(on Zoom)**\n\n\\*Original Lyrics and Songs by Songwriter and Producer Steve Flemming\n\n\\*Story songs\, love songs\, spiritual songs\, songs about nature\, our culture\, our past\, our future\, relationships and our lives\n\nI'll be playing a mix of songs using a fusion of mixed genres like\, **Folk\, Traditional Folk\, Country\, Blue Grass\, Singer Song Writer\, Soft Rock\, Easy Listening\, Classic Rock\, R & B\, Gospel\, Pop\, Adult Contemporary\, Indie Rock/Po**p and many others genres too. So please sit back and get ready to have an amazing auditory experience in the comforts of your own home :)\n\n\\*You can come on and off at any time during the night- starting at 8:30 pm\n\n**About Steve Flemming:**\nHighly influenced by the great singer songwriters of the 50s\, 60s\, 70s\, 80s and 90s. I have been writing my own songs since 1990. Songs about life\, love\, loss\, hope\, faith\, joy\, romance\, memories\, spirituality and heartbreak. Songs that are universal\, heartfelt and often relevant to the lives of many others.\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Event Fee:**\n\n**Pay What You Can: (P.W.Y.C)**\nYou can kindly send through e transfer or pay pal to:\n**steveflemming11@gmail.com**\n\n-Anything you can contribute is greatly appreciated to help support this meaningful musical endeavor and song loving community\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Zoom link:**\n\nhttps://us04web.zoom.us/j/495043928\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\n**Testimonials from Past Events:**\nYour songs are wonder-full\, speak to emotions\, experiences and moments we've all felt and lived. S. B.\nSteve Flemming is an amazing songwriter whose lyrics stir the soul. He transforms everyday thoughts and life into beautiful poetry and magical tunes. Amazing stuff yet again Steve. - L.L.\nSteve\, thank you for a night of heartfelt\, exhilarating\, and inspiring music.\nV.R.\nThanks for having me my friend. I love your words\, they calm me and energize me at the same time I'll look forward to your next invite\nM.Z.\nThese great songs definitely helped me to decompress after a long day. Keep up the song writing Steve\, these are great! - S.S.\nThank you so much for a relaxing evening and sharing your inspiring music Steve! I am excited to hear more and I hope you do this again!! - C.B\nLovely songs and a great vibe with wonderful people. I couldn’t have asked for a better way to close my day. Huge thanks Steve\, for inviting me! I truly enjoyed every moment! - N.A.\nThe lyrics are amazing. From the heart...\nThanks Steve for the amazing tunes. I'm truly blown away. Very glad I joined.\n\\- E\\.E\\.\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
