SUMMARY:The SATURDAY NIGHT ALL GREEN ST. PADDY'S BASH! (Pubs\, Band\, DJ & Dancing)
DESCRIPTION:Soul City Social Club (Toronto\, Canada)\nHello everyone\,\n\n**Kindly Read Carefully:**\n\nPlease join us for a unique **St. Paddy's** experience as we hit\, not one but two great places to mix\, mingle and dance the night away with Live Music\, Band\, DJ and awesome people!\n\nFirst we will meet at ***Duke of Kent (2nd Floor) You can ask the hostess at the front to direct you to Steve's group upstairs)*** (Conveniently located extremely close Yonge & Eglinton corner. (2 minute walk north from the subway station)\n\nThe next venue is only minutes away from there (secret location)\n\n**Where to Meet us?**\n**Duke of Kent:** You will be directed upstairs to there cool party room area :)\n**Date:** Saturday March 14th\, 2026\n**Address:** 2315 Yonge Street Toronto\, ON M4P 2X9\n**Arrive between:** 6:00 pm and 7:45 pm (if you can)\n(Encouraged earlier rather than later to have a chance to meet everyone and soak up a great Saturday night)\n\n**Highlights:**\n\\*Reserved tables and seating for dinner\, cocktails and mingling\n\\*Venue is very close to the Yonge and Eglinton subway station\n\\*Ice breaker game to make it easy to meet and connect with everyone :)\n\\*A fun game to win complimentary beverages :)\n\\*Live Music (Band) (DJ) and dancing at our second secret location\n\n\\*Dress casual or dress up if you like :)\n**DRESS IN Green and have a Chance to win Sweets and Treats :)**\n\n-Joined by my other social groups too\; so we can anticipate an awesome St. Paddy's Bash to remember!\n\n\\*One beverage or appetizer minimum at the first and second location-(No loitering please)\nThank you very much and remember to Tip your Servers :)\n\\*a 3rd venue may be an option too depending on how everyone is feeling :)\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\nEvent Details below:\n\nSteve Flemming\n(Organizer/Host)\nhttps://www.meetup.com/soulcity/\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\nEvent Details:\n**The SATURDAY NIGHT ALL GREEN ST. PADDY'S BASH!**\n**(Pubs\, Band\, DJ & Dancing)**\n\n-We will meet ***upstairs in their party bar room area\;*** connect with everyone\, ice breaker game\, socialize\, share some laughs\, then make our way new our surprise location with live music\, DJ\, super fun atmosphere\, great people and dancing :)\n\\*Plan to come for dinner too if you like at the first venue\, as tables will be reserved for everyone\n\n(All Venues will be close walking distance for us)\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**EVENT FEE:**\n\n**Night of Event- Saturday March 14th (Arrival Times)**\n\n**\\*Ladies and Gents- Dress in Green if you can :)**\n-10 dollars if you arrive between (6:00 pm and 7:30 pm)\n-15 dollars if you arrive between (7:31 pm and 8:50 pm)\n\nIf you arrive after that you will simply miss the event :)\n**(cash or by e transfer to steveflemming11@gmail.com)**\n\n**DRESS IN GREEN and have a Chance to Win! :)**\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
