SUMMARY:St. Paddy's Day Celebration! (DJ and Dancing) (Tuesday\, March 17th)
DESCRIPTION:Soul City Social Club (Toronto\, Canada)\nGood day everyone\,\n\nPlease join us for a fantastic **St. Paddy's Celebration\;** as we mix\, mingle\, dance the night away to all our favorite songs!\n\n\\*Joined by my other social groups too\; so we can anticipate a terrific turn out with lots of friendly peers to enjoy dinner and the lively dance floor!\n\n**Date:** Tuesday March 17th\, 2026\n**Location:** 747 Mt. Pleasant (Smoke Show)\n\n**\\*Meet us inside Smoke Show between 7:30 pm and 9:00 pm**\n\\*If you have to arrive after that\, still let the front door staff know you are with **Steve's group** so they can direct you to us!\n\n(Event Details Below)\n\nSincerely\,\n\nSteve Flemming\n(Organizer/Host )\n\nEvent Details:\n**St. Paddy's Day Celebration! (DJ and Dancing) (Tuesday\, March 17th)**\n\n-A fun\, interactive\, event with friends\, food\, cocktails\, green beer\, reserved seating\, DJ and Dancing!\n-Pool Table available\n-DJ\, Song Requests\, Mingling and Dancing\n-Plenty of parking all around the venue\n\\*For more information on the menu please refer to the Smoke Show menu https://www.smokeshowbbqandbrew.com/\n\n**Event Fee:**\n5 dollars if you're **wearing green** (cash or in advance by e transfer)\n10 dollars when you arrive not wearing green\n(cash or e transfer in advance to [Steveflemming11@gmail.com](http://Steveflemming11@gmail.com/))\n(Beverage or Appetizer Minimum please)\n\n**Friendly Reminders:**\n**-Arrive any time between 7:30 pm and 9:00 pm inside the restaurant (ask or look for Steve/Organizer when you arrive)**\n\n\\*Just a 2 minute walk now from the new Eglinton and Mount Pleasant station :)
